def split_train_validation(dataframe, split_size):
  test_size = int(len(dataframe) * split_size)
  train = dataframe[:-test_size]
  validation = dataframe[-test_size:]
  return train, validation
In [ ]:
class Cryptocurrency():
  def __init__(self, symbol, currency, data_source, start, prediction_days, future_days):
    self.symbol = symbol
    self.currency = currency
    self.data_source = data_source
    self.start = start
    self.prediction_days = prediction_days
    self.future_days = future_days
    self.read_data()
  
  def read_data(self):
    self.df = web.DataReader(f'{self.symbol}-{self.currency}', self.data_source, self.start, datetime.now().strftime('%d/%m/%Y'))
    self.df.drop(['Adj Close'], axis=1, inplace=True)
    self.df['Future Price'] = self.df[['Close']].shift(-self.future_days)

  def data_preparation(self, scaler, split_size):
    self.train, self.validation = split_train_validation(self.df, split_size)
    self.train, self.validation = self.train['Close'], self.validation['Close']
    scaled_data = scaler.fit_transform(self.train.values.reshape(-1, 1))
    x_train, t_train = [], []
    for x in range(self.prediction_days, len(scaled_data) - self.future_days):
        x_train.append(scaled_data[x - self.prediction_days:x, 0])
        t_train.append(scaled_data[x + self.future_days, 0])
    x_train, t_train = np.array(x_train), np.array(t_train)
    x_train = np.reshape(x_train, (x_train.shape[0], x_train.shape[1], 1))
    return x_train, t_train

  def correlation_to_target(self):
    return self.df['Close'].corr(self.df['Future Price'])

class Cryptocurrencies():
  def __init__(self, symbols, currency, data_source, start, prediction_days, future_days):
    self.currency = currency
    self.data_source = data_source
    self.start = start
    self.prediction_days = prediction_days
    self.future_days = future_days
    self.init_cryptocurrencies(symbols)

  def init_cryptocurrencies(self, symbols):
    self.symbols = []
    self.cryptocurrencies = []

    for symbol in symbols:
      cryptocurrency = Cryptocurrency(symbol, self.currency, self.data_source, self.start, self.prediction_days, self.future_days)
      if cryptocurrency.correlation_to_target() > 0.97:
        self.symbols.append(symbol)
        self.cryptocurrencies.append(cryptocurrency)
        
  def display_all_heatmaps(self):
    num_of_coins = len(self.cryptocurrencies)
    coin_index = 0
    num_of_cols = 3
    num_of_rows = math.ceil(num_of_coins / num_of_cols)
    fig, axes = plt.subplots(num_of_rows, num_of_cols)
    plt.subplots_adjust(top=4.5, bottom=0, left=0, right=3)

    for i in range(num_of_rows):
      for j in range(num_of_cols):
        ax = sns.heatmap(np.abs(self.cryptocurrencies[coin_index].df.corr()), cmap=plt.cm.Blues, ax=axes[i, j])
        ax.set_title(label=f'{self.symbols[coin_index]}-{self.currency}', fontsize=10)
        coin_index += 1
        if coin_index >= num_of_coins:
          break

    for i in range(num_of_coins, num_of_rows * num_of_cols):
      fig.delaxes(axes.flatten()[i])

  def currencies_correlations(self):
    all_crypto_df = pd.DataFrame(data=[coin.df['Close'].values for coin in self.cryptocurrencies], index=self.symbols).T
    corr = np.abs(all_crypto_df.corr())
    plt.figure(figsize=(20, 14))
    sns.heatmap(corr, annot=True, cmap=plt.cm.Blues, vmin=0, vmax=1)
    plt.title('Correlations Between Currencies', fontsize=16)
    plt.show()

    subsets = []
    for coin in corr.index:
      coin_corr = []
      is_sub_exist = False
      for i in range(len(corr[coin])):
        if corr[coin][i] > 0.8:
          coin_corr.append(corr[coin].index[i])
      if len(coin_corr) > 2:
        for sub in subsets:
          if sub == coin_corr:
            is_sub_exist = True
            break
        if not is_sub_exist:
          subsets.append(coin_corr)
    return subsets

In [ ]:
units = 50
dropout = 0.2
output_units = 1
optimizer = 'adam'
loss = 'mean_squared_error'

LSTM Model

In [ ]:
def get_lstm_model(x_train):
  model = Sequential()
  model.add(LSTM(units=units, return_sequences=True, input_shape=(x_train.shape[1], 1)))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(LSTM(units=units, return_sequences=True))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(LSTM(units=units))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(Dense(units=output_units))
  model.compile(optimizer = optimizer, loss = loss)
  return model

Bidirectional LSTM Model

In [ ]:
def get_bidirectional_lstm_model(x_train):
  model = Sequential()
  model.add(LSTM(units, return_sequences=True, input_shape=(x_train.shape[1], 1)))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(Bidirectional(LSTM(units, return_sequences=True)))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(Bidirectional(LSTM(units)))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(Dense(units=output_units))
  model.compile(optimizer = optimizer, loss = loss)
  return model

GRU Model

In [ ]:
def get_gru_model(x_train):
  model = Sequential()
  model.add(GRU(units=units, return_sequences=True, input_shape=(x_train.shape[1], 1)))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(GRU(units=units, return_sequences=True))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(GRU(units=units))
  model.add(Dropout(dropout))
  model.add(Dense(units=output_units))
  model.compile(optimizer = optimizer, loss = loss)
  return model

In [ ]:
epochs = 30
batch_size = 42
models = {}

for cryptocurrency in cryptocurrencies.cryptocurrencies:
  scaler = MinMaxScaler(feature_range=(0, 1))
  x_train, t_train = cryptocurrency.data_preparation(scaler, 0.2)

  print('-'*20, cryptocurrency.symbol, '-', 'LSTM', '-'*20)
  lstm_model = get_lstm_model(x_train)
  lstm_model.fit(x_train, t_train, epochs=epochs, batch_size=batch_size)

  print('-'*20, cryptocurrency.symbol, '-', 'Bidirectional LSTM', '-'*20)
  bidirectional_lstm_model = get_bidirectional_lstm_model(x_train)
  bidirectional_lstm_model.fit(x_train, t_train, epochs=epochs, batch_size=batch_size)

  print('-'*20, cryptocurrency.symbol, '-', 'GRU', '-'*20)
  gru_model = get_gru_model(x_train)
  gru_model.fit(x_train, t_train, epochs=epochs, batch_size=batch_size)

  models[cryptocurrency.symbol] = {
      'LSTM': lstm_model,
      'Bidirectional LSTM': bidirectional_lstm_model,
      'GRU': gru_model
  }
  print()

Evaluation and Save Model to File¶

In [ ]:
best_models = {}

for cryptocurrency in cryptocurrencies.cryptocurrencies:
  test_data = cryptocurrency.validation.values
  actual_prices = test_data[prediction_days:]
  model_inputs = np.array(test_data)
  model_inputs = model_inputs.reshape(-1, 1)
  model_inputs = scaler.fit_transform(model_inputs)

  x_test = []

  for x in range(prediction_days, len(model_inputs)):
    x_test.append(model_inputs[x-prediction_days:x, 0])

  x_test = np.array(x_test)
  x_test = np.reshape(x_test, (x_test.shape[0], x_test.shape[1], 1))

  best_models[cryptocurrency.symbol] = 'LSTM'
  min_mape = 40
  plt.figure(figsize=(20, 4))
  for i, model in enumerate(models[cryptocurrency.symbol]):
    prediction_prices = models[cryptocurrency.symbol][model].predict(x_test)
    prediction_prices = scaler.inverse_transform(prediction_prices)
    prediction_prices = prediction_prices.flatten()
    rmse = float(math.sqrt(tf.keras.metrics.mean_squared_error(actual_prices, prediction_prices)))
    mape = float(tf.keras.metrics.mean_absolute_percentage_error(actual_prices, prediction_prices))
    plt.subplot(1, 3, i + 1)
    plt.plot(actual_prices, color='black', label='Actual Prices')
    plt.plot(prediction_prices, color='green', label='Predicted Prices')
    plt.title(f'{model} RMSE: {"{:.2f}".format(rmse)} MAPE: {"{:.2f}".format(mape)}')
    plt.xlabel('Time')
    plt.ylabel('Price')
    plt.legend(loc='upper left')

    if mape < min_mape:
      min_mape = mape
      best_models[cryptocurrency.symbol] = { 'model': model, 'accuracy': 100 - min_mape }
  print('\n', '-'*20, cryptocurrency.symbol, '-'*20)
  plt.show()

coins = {}

for cryptocurrency in cryptocurrencies.cryptocurrencies:
  if cryptocurrency.symbol in best_models:
    scaler = MinMaxScaler(feature_range=(0, 1))
    scaled_data = scaler.fit_transform(cryptocurrency.df['Close'].values.reshape(-1, 1))
    x_train, t_train = [], []
    for x in range(prediction_days, len(scaled_data) - future_days):
        x_train.append(scaled_data[x - prediction_days:x, 0])
        t_train.append(scaled_data[x + future_days, 0])
    x_train, t_train = np.array(x_train), np.array(t_train)
    x_train = np.reshape(x_train, (x_train.shape[0], x_train.shape[1], 1))

    if best_models[cryptocurrency.symbol]['model'] == 'LSTM':
      model = get_lstm_model(x_train)
    elif best_models[cryptocurrency.symbol]['model'] == 'Bidirectional LSTM':
      model = get_bidirectional_lstm_model(x_train)
    elif best_models[cryptocurrency.symbol]['model'] == 'GRU':
      model = get_gru_model(x_train) 

    print('-'*20, cryptocurrency.symbol, '-'*20)
    model.fit(x_train, t_train, epochs=epochs, batch_size=batch_size)
    model.save(cryptocurrency.symbol)
    coins[cryptocurrency.symbol] = { 'accuracy': best_models[cryptocurrency.symbol]['accuracy'] }

with open('coins.json', 'w') as f:
    json.dump(coins, f)
